graph TB
    subgraph "MLflow Operator"
        Controller[MLflow Controller]
        ConfigController[MLflowConfig Controller]
        HelmRenderer[Helm Renderer]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy Manager]
        TLSManager[TLS Certificate Manager]

        Controller -->|uses| HelmRenderer
        Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
        Controller -->|manages| TLSManager
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        MLflowCR[MLflow CR<br/>mlflow.opendatahub.io/v1]
        MLflowConfigCR[MLflowConfig CR<br/>mlflow.kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Deployed Resources"
        MLflowDeployment[MLflow Server Deployment]
        MLflowService[MLflow Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        HTTPRoute[Gateway HTTPRoute]
        ConsoleLink[OpenShift ConsoleLink]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]
        TLSSecret[mlflow-tls Secret]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL Database<br/>5432/TCP TLS]
        S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        ServiceCA[OpenShift service-ca]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        Notebooks[Notebooks/Workbenches]
        DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
        TrainingOp[Training Operator]
        ModelReg[Model Registry]
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| MLflowCR
    User -->|creates| MLflowConfigCR

    MLflowCR -->|watched by| Controller
    MLflowConfigCR -->|watched by| ConfigController

    Controller -->|creates| MLflowDeployment
    Controller -->|creates| MLflowService
    Controller -->|creates| HTTPRoute
    Controller -->|creates| ConsoleLink
    Controller -->|creates| PVC

    ServiceCA -->|injects cert| TLSSecret
    MLflowService -->|annotated for| ServiceCA

    MLflowDeployment -->|uses| TLSSecret
    MLflowDeployment -->|connects to| PostgreSQL
    MLflowDeployment -->|stores artifacts| S3
    MLflowDeployment -->|authenticates via| K8sAPI

    Notebooks -->|tracks experiments| MLflowDeployment
    DSPipelines -->|logs metrics| MLflowDeployment
    TrainingOp -->|tracks training| MLflowDeployment
    MLflowDeployment -.->|alternative to| ModelReg

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style ConfigController fill:#4a90e2
    style HelmRenderer fill:#4a90e2
    style MLflowCR fill:#f5a623
    style MLflowConfigCR fill:#f5a623
    style PostgreSQL fill:#999
    style S3 fill:#999
    style K8sAPI fill:#999
    style ServiceCA fill:#999
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321
    style TrainingOp fill:#7ed321
    style ModelReg fill:#7ed321
